        "paragraph_index": 0,
        "text": "## Distribution of Constant Types in SRD-46 Stability Measurements\n\nThe NIST SRD-46 database contains **79,063** stability constant measurements, distributed across three constant types:\n\n| Constant Type | Count | Percentage |\n|---------------|---------|------------|\n| **K** (stepwise equilibrium constant) | 60,540 | 76.57% |\n| **H** (protonation/hydrolysis constant) | 9,693 | 12.26% |\n| **S** (overall stability constant, β) | 8,830 | 11.17% |",
